oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Alan Jabbour and the Morgan family at the Tennessee Folklore Society's 50th anniversary
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Musician and folklorist Alan Jabbour performs with members of the Morgan family at the 50th anniversary celebration of the Tennessee Folklore Society, Cookeville, 1984. The image includes Scott Morgan, Alan Jabbour, and Tom Morgan with John Hartford, Mary Morgan, and Richard Blaustein in the background, obscured.
